{!<tr><td><div class="box" style='background-color:#FA5A42'> </div> !} AP: {!</td><td>!} [+ ap_election_votes_salzburg +]% {!</td><td>!} [+ ap_seats_salzburg +] ([+ ap_zl +]%) {!</td></tr>!}

{!<tr><td><div class="box" style='background-color:#0E428E'> </div> !} DNLP: {!</td><td>!} [+ dnlp_election_votes_salzburg +]% {!</td><td>!} [+ dnlp_seats_salzburg +] ([+ dnlp_zl +]%) {!</td></tr>!}

[? if ovp_exist: {!<tr><td><div class="box" style='background-color:#000000'> </div> !} ÖVP: {!</td><td>!} [+ ovp_election_votes_salzburg +]% {!</td><td>!} [+ ovp_seats_salzburg +] ([+ ovp_zl +]%) {!</td></tr>!} ?]

{!<tr><td><div class="box" style='background-color:#ED2939'> </div> !} VF: {!</td><td>!} [+ vf_election_votes_salzburg +]% {!</td><td>!} [+ vf_seats_salzburg +] ([+ vf_zl +]%) {!</td></tr>!}

{!<tr><td><div class="box" style='background-color:#909090'> </div> !} Other: {!</td><td>!} [+ other_election_votes_salzburg +]% {!</td><td>!} [+ other_seats_salzburg +] ([+ other_zl +]%) {!</td></tr>!}
{!</table>!}

**Potential coalitions:**

Right Coalition (<span style="color: #EEEE22;">**[+ oclk_name +]**</span> + <span style="color: #ED2939;">**VF**</span>[? if ovp_exist: + <span style="color: #000000;">**ÖVP**</span>?]): [+ right_coalition_salzburg +]%

There are some potential coalition arrangements.

@coalition_menu

- @oclk_majority
- @vf_majority
- @right_coalition
- @no_majority

@no_majority
title: There is no clear governing majority.
view-if: vf_seats_salzburg <= 15 and oclk_seats_salzburg <= 15 and right_coalition_salzburg <= 50

The previous coalition continues to govern as a minority government.



@vf_majority
title: The <span style="color: #ED2939;">**VF**</span> forms a majority government.
subtitle: <span style="color: #ED2939;">**VF**</span> ([+ vf_zl +]%)
view-if: vf_seats_salzburg > 15
on-arrival: {!
Q.salzburg_oclk = 0;
Q.salzburg_vf = 1;

Q.in_right_coalition_salzburg = 0;
Q.in_vf_majority_salzburg = 1;
Q.in_oclk_majority_salzburg = 0;
!}

